{
  "stem": "10587.6",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Funfteichen, I was there a year and a few months.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Except that there was a lot of beating going on there, too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This-- this Sturmbannfuhrer Schamal was a sadist.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He used to-- he used to grab people by the shirt and-- and pull towards you, and then let it loose and used to hit you with the elbows in your face.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that Schamal knocked four teeth in my mouth, knocked out four teeth.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Also, he would take a shovel, like a spade, and he would hit you on-- in the back of your calf, legs.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was doing something, I was carrying something, and I did not-- you had to take off your hat and-- like a salute and look-- look-- look him in-- in the eyes-- and I was carrying something in camp and I-- could have been a bale of hay or something.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was doing a special commander work, and-- and-- and every time, so he just get up, so one time when he hit me like that with the right elbow, and then when I got up he did the same thing with the left elbow.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was bleeding.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he says, this is better than a bullet, because a bullet costs money.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He mumbled in-- to me in German, and I understand German, so I know exactly what he was talking.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And another time I was doing some work and he hit me in the back of my calves, on the leg.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he used to-- that-- that hurts quite a bit.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I've seen-- I was lucky enough-- because I've seen him where he would hit people with a shovel, on your throat, or on your head.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
